Thank you for submitting a pull request! 

All kinds of pull request are welcome: improving styles, fixing bugs, better cross-platform performance, improved UI, and so on. 

For larger contributions, please get in touch before making changes - you can open a discussion or issue on this repo.

For small changes such as improving sentence structure, grammar fixes, minor updates for new three.js versions, errata or other changes, go right ahead :) 

